  "label": "Bastion Rell",
  "description": "This individual is an undead human of cavernous provenance, defined by a light skinTone stretched taut over prominent bone and hollowed cheeks. Gray eyes sit deep beneath a heavy brow ridge, and black hair falls in an unkempt mat that frames a rigid jawline. The mouth sets in a permanent slackness that exposes darkened gums and broken teeth, while the hands show long, rigid fingers with cracked nails. Movement follows a repetitive, ritualized pattern typical of the Obsidian Scar’s revenant dead, and the presence registers as implacable and unresponsive to ordinary social cues.",
